<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.6.9">
<l>aḷantiṭṭa tūṇai yavaṉṟaṭṭa vāṅkē</l>
<l>vaḷarntiṭṭu vāḷukirc ciṅka vuruvā</l>
<l>yuḷantoṭ ṭiraṇiya ṉoṇmār vakalam</l>
<l>piḷantiṭṭa kaikaḷāl cappāṇi pēymulai yuṇṭāṉē cappāṇi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[Clap] cappāṇi with the hands that,</l>
<l rend="indent">when [he] struck the post that had been measured and erected there,</l>
<l rend="indent">you who had grown in the form of a lion with sharp claws,</l>
<l>dug out the heart of Hiraṇya, splitting the width of [his] bright chest,</l>
<l>You who drank from the breast of the demon, [clap] cappāṇi!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
